author: Adam Shaw, Ben Evansky
title: Trump administration urges UN Security Council to state coronavirus originated in China
description: The Trump administration is pushing to add language to a coronavirus resolution at the U.N. Security Council that would say explicitly that the virus originated in China -- part of the administration’s efforts to keep the focus on the communist regime.
